
# MultiSafepay 
![multisafepay](https://static.openfintech.io/vendors/multisafepay/logo.svg?w=400&c=v0.59.26#w200)  

## General 
 
**Code:** `multisafepay` 
 
**Name:** 
 
:	[EN] MultiSafepay 
 
**Status:** `active` 
 
**Description:** 
 
: [EN]  MultiSafepay is a leading Payment Service Provider in the Netherlands. Since 1999, we have provided pioneering online payment services to thousands of online businesses across Europe.  MultiSafepay offers a wide range of online payment methods, integration options, and conversion increasing tools. By signing just one contract, you manage all your online payments and every MultiSafepay tool and feature designed to help your online business thrive. Our services include online and mobile payments, Mail Order Telephone Order (MOTO), subscription payments, and more. Additionally, we offer extensive support including a personal account manager, skilled tech support, and customer service. You can access all tools and features in your personalized account with MultiSafepay Control. Or download the unique app (available in iOS and Android) so you can access your account on your smart phone or tablet and manage your online business anytime and anywhere.
